headline: CF Industries Holdings, Inc. to Participate in Upcoming Investor Conference
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., February 24, 2025--CF Industries Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: CF) today announced that the Company will present at the BofA 2025 Global Agriculture and Materials Conference at 1:15 pm ET on Wednesday, February 26, 2025.

headline: BofA upgrades CF Industries on improved nitrogen market, risk/reward
summary: Investing.com -- Bank of America upgraded CF Industries (NYSE:CF) to "Neutral" from "Underperform" given a more balanced risk/reward profile following the company's post-earnings sell-off and improving nitrogen market fundamentals.
